data.name: books
data.value:
[
  {{#repeat 1000}}
  {
    "id": "{{faker 'string.uuid'}}",
    "imageUrl": "{{faker 'image.urlLoremFlickr' width=178 height=255}}",
    "author": "{{faker 'book.author'}}",
    "title": "{{faker 'book.title'}}",
    "price": {{faker 'number.float' min=1 max=500 fractionDigits=2}},
    "publisher": "{{faker 'book.publisher'}}",
    "isbn": "{{faker 'commerce.isbn'}}",
    "sku": "{{faker 'number.int'}}",
    "publicationYear": "{{faker 'number.int' min=1000 max=2025}}",
    "pages": "{{faker 'number.int' min=10 max=5000}}",
    "weight": "{{faker 'number.float' min=10 max=10 fractionDigits=2}}",
    "height": "{{faker 'number.float' min=10 max=10 fractionDigits=2}}",
    "targetAge": "{{faker 'number.int' min=10 max=100}}",
    "synopsis": "{{lorem 300}}",
    "genre": "{{oneOf (array 'manga')}}"
  }
  {{/repeat}}
]
